      "file_path": "docker-compose/docker-compose.yml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 52,
      "message": "Yeah so it's going to default to 30000 unless the environment variable ADVISED_MODULES_SYNC_SLEEP_TIME_MS has been set. If the docker image is brought up without the CSITs it will be 30 seconds. The CSITs set the environment variable to 2000 so it will be 2 seconds during the CSITs",
